fields.name: greek-island-hopping
fields.description: Choose your islands, grab your white linen and reenact Mamma Mia in this 3-week island hopping adventure!
fields.itinerary:

fields.name: wavehunters
fields.description: Pick up your board and ride the waves! Whether you're a newbie or an experienced pro, enjoy the best surf of your life!
fields.itinerary:
• Day 1: Enjoy a full-day lesson with ex-pro surfers followed by dinner on the beach!
  • Day 2: Free day! Spend the day practising your newly learnt skills or explore the local town
  • Day 3: Group surf day. Time to get to know your fellow travellers with a day on the water. Finish the day with a night out with your new friends!

fields.name: underwater-excursion
fields.description: Come and join us in an underwater world of adventure! Get scuba diving certified and be prepared to dive into a world of beauty!

fields.name: finding-your-zen
fields.description: Take a deep breath and relax your mind as you join us on this meditation retreat. There's no better place to get realigned and feel refreshed!
fields.itinerary:
• Day 1: Afternoon mud bath, followed by a sunset beach walk - dinner served on the beach
  • Day 2: Morning meditation with yogi followed by lunch in the gardens, ending the day with dinner at a local restaurant
  • Day 3: Sunrise massage and breakfast in the garden followed by afternoon meditation

fields.name: wine-not
fields.description: Come and get a taste of what these Mediterranean wineries have to offer! With stunning views and wonderful food, it'll be an adventure to remember ... or not!!!
fields.itinerary:
• Day 1: Adega do Cantor Winery, followed by dinner in Albufeira overlooking the Portuguese Algarve
  • Day 2: Travel day to Spain with stops along the way. Dinner and free time in the evening to explore Barcelona!
  • Day 3: Caves Codorniu Winery with a 3-course meal and tasting in the evening
  • Day 4: Travel day to France with stops along the way. Dinner and free time in the evening to stroll around the picturesque fishing village of Bandol
  • Day 5: Bandol Winery, followed by dinner at a local fondue restaurant
  • Day 6: Travel day to Italy with stops along the way. Dinner and free time in the beautiful historic city of Florence
  • Day 7: Tenuta Di Capezzana Winery followed by dinner at Ciro and Sons in Florence
